install
=======
- At, first.

  - modify make file for your environment especially cv++ in makefile.
  - cv++ is opencv building support c compiling command.
  - https://github.com/mattak/setup/blob/master/bin/cv++

::
  
  make
  make localbin # install for $HOME/bin

